        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Jehovah, who speaks and doth, and need no more than will to work and accomplish; so he made, sustaineth, and disposeth of all. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
