      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "And it shall melt, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " as snow before the sun in its hottest influences, or as wax before a mighty fire. He who can do this, can do all that I have denounced against you, O Israel. The rest of the verse, see ",
